data.description:
Introducing this exceptional main floor unit located in the heart of Greenwood Village/Denver Tech Center. Step inside to discover a spacious open kitchen and dining room, perfect for entertaining. This home boasts 2 bedrooms, a full bath, and a convenient walk-in closet. The large family room features a cozy gas fireplace and opens up to a private and gated patio, creating an inviting outdoor space.

One of the highlights of this property is its rare offering of not one but TWO garages, providing ample storage and parking options. Experience the luxury vinyl wood flooring that flows throughout, adding a touch of elegance to every room. All appliances have been thoughtfully updated, including a new air conditioner, furnace with whole home humidifier, washer and dryer. Additionally, the kitchen and bathroom cabinets have been beautifully refaced, complemented by new quartz countertops in both areas.

Located within the Cherry Creek School District, this home offers access to excellent education opportunities. Enjoy neighborhood amenities such as a pool and fitness center, as well as the convenience of nearby restaurants and shopping options within walking distance. With its close proximity to transit and light rail, commuting is made easy.

Whether you're looking for an ideal place to call home or seeking an investment property with great potential, this residence has it all. Don't miss out on this rare opportunity - schedule a showing today!
